Proposal will require vaccine passports for:
- Nightclubs;
- Hospitality;
- Cinemas, theatres and conferences;
- Indoor events with 500 or more;
- Outdoor events with 4000 or more;
- Events where more than 10,000 people will be present.

New survey out from @NIjobscom on pandemic's impact on our work attitudes: 
▪️ 68% are reassessing their career;
▪️ 71% now expect employers to offer remote or hybrid working;
▪️ 68% say flexible work is now more important to them than job security.

