New tourism stats from NISRA*:
▪️ 500k hotel rooms sold in year-to-Apr ’21 (-77%)
▪️ 67k B&amp;B/guesthouse rooms sold year-to-Apr ’21 (-83%);
▪️ 1.1m air passengers year-to-Mar ’21 (vs 9.2m peak in 2019);
▪️ 429k caravans crossed the border in year-to-May '21, the highest since 2014

